      "content": "i never thought i'd hear someone say that. it's just so hard because everyone keeps telling me to \"be brave\" and \"hold on,\" but they don't understand how exhausting it is. it feels like they're asking me to stay in a burning building. why does everyone make it seem like staying in pain is some kind of victory?",
